longBusinessSummary: VERBIO Vereinigte BioEnergie AG produces and supplies biofuels in Germany and rest of Europe. The company's products include biodiesel, bioethanol, biomethane, bioglycerin, and liquid fertilizers. It offers its products to oil corporations, oil traders, independent filling stations, haulage companies, public utilities, and vehicle fleets. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Leipzig, Germany.
